==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Cor
<hw>Cor</hw> <pr>(k⟦ocir⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Heb.
<ets>k⟦omac⟧r</ets>.]</ety> <def>A Hebrew measure of capacity; a
